---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Com funciona - Ara què?">
  <main class="pt-24 pb-20 bg-white">
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 mb-24">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 space-y-4">
        <h1
          class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-900 leading-tight"
        >
          Descobreix <span class="text-[#A7D6E9]">Ara què?</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium">
          Mira com la nostra aplicació ajuda a millorar l'autonomia diària
          mitjançant una interfície visual i intuïtiva.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative aspect-video w-full rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl shadow-sky-100 border-8 border-white overflow-hidden"
      >
        <iframe
          class="w-full h-full"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/B9QfVKaB4NQ"
          title="Ara Què? Demo"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 space-y-3">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tighter italic"
        >
          Funcionament Bàsic
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1.5 bg-[#F9C18A] mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/50 flex flex-col items-center border border-slate-100 transition-all hover:border-[#A7D6E9]/30"
        >
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#A7D6E9]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8"
          >
            <span class="text-2xl">🔑</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4 text-center">
            Accés senzill
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm text-center leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Sistema d'entrada optimitzat per a usuaris i supervisors amb perfils
            diferenciats.
          </p>
          <ul
            class="w-full space-y-3 text-xs text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-50 pt-6"
          >
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 italic">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#A7D6E9] rounded-full"></span>
              Perfil personalitzat per a l'usuari
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 italic">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#A7D6E9] rounded-full"></span>
              Panell de control per al tutor
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/50 flex flex-col items-center border border-slate-100 transition-all hover:border-[#F9C18A]/30"
        >
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#F9C18A]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8"
          >
            <span class="text-2xl">🖼️</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4 text-center">
            Guia Visual
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm text-center leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Ús de pictogrames d'ARASAAC per facilitar la comprensió de cada
            tasca.
          </p>
          <ul
            class="w-full space-y-3 text-xs text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-50 pt-6"
          >
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 italic">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#F9C18A] rounded-full"></span>
              Imatges clares i estandarditzades
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 italic">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#F9C18A] rounded-full"></span>
              Colors associats per categories
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/50 flex flex-col items-center border border-slate-100 transition-all hover:border-[#A7D6E9]/30"
        >
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#A7D6E9]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8"
          >
            <span class="text-2xl">👣</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4 text-center">
            Rutes guiades
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm text-center leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Les rutines es divideixen en passes petites per no aclaparar
            l'usuari.
          </p>
          <ul
            class="w-full space-y-3 text-xs text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-50 pt-6"
          >
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 italic">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#A7D6E9] rounded-full"></span>
              Seqüències lògiques diàries
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 italic">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#A7D6E9] rounded-full"></span>
              Confirmació de tasca feta
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
